Package: pohoda-digest
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>
Installed-Size: 71
Depends: php-cli, php-vitexsoftware-digest-modules (>= 1.0), php-vitexsoftware-digest-renderer (>= 1.0), php-vitexsoftware-pohoda-connector (>= 2.0), composer, cron
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/VitexSoftware/Pohoda-Digest
Description: Analytics and reporting tool for Money S3/Pohoda accounting
 Pohoda-Digest is a comprehensive analytics and reporting tool for Money S3
 and Pohoda accounting systems. It generates detailed financial reports,
 monitors business metrics, and provides insights through various modules.
 .
 Features:
  * Integration with Money S3/Pohoda via mServer
  * Modular analytics system
  * HTML reports with multiple themes
  * Command-line interface for automation
  * Cron-ready for scheduled reporting
  * Outcoming invoices analysis
  * Customer debt monitoring
  * Customizable report generation
